Our special features:

1) Beautifully coloured buttons, with active background!
If player presses an illegal button, button will be red until he releases.
Otherwise, button will turn green.

2)
Player can cancel last button selected, by pressing the button with
the right-click.

3)
The amazing refresh button!
If player finds no more words and has time left over, he can try his luck
with a new board!
Score and all words guessed are kept.

4)
Well designed text box!
Player cannot manually add words to text box. If words reach end of text box,
player can scroll through text box to see all of his words.


